msgid ""
"You typically need two dump datasets: one from the \"problem side\" (the run"
" that exposes the accuracy or numerical error) and another from the "
"\"benchmark side\" (a good baseline). These datasets do not have to be "
"identical—they can come from different branches, framework versions, or even"
" alternative implementations (operator substitutions, different graph-"
"optimization switches, etc.). As long as they use the same or similar "
"inputs, hardware topology, and sampling points (step/token), `msprobe` can "
"compare them and locate the divergent nodes. If you cannot find a perfectly "
"clean benchmark, start by capturing the problem-side data, craft the "
"smallest reproducible case by hand, and perform a self-comparison. Below we "
"assume the problem dump is `problem_dump` and the benchmark dump is "
"`bench_dump`."
msgstr ""
"通常需要两个采集数据集：一个来自“问题侧”（暴露精度或数值错误的运行），另一个来自“基准侧”（良好的基线）。这些数据集不必完全相同——它们可以来自不同的分支、框架版本，甚至不同的实现（算子替换、不同的图优化开关等）。只要它们使用相同或相似的输入、硬件拓扑和采样点（步数/token），`msprobe`"
" 就能进行比较并定位差异节点。如果找不到完全干净的基准，可以先采集问题侧数据，手动构建最小可复现案例，然后进行自比较。下文中，我们假设问题采集目录为 "
"`problem_dump`，基准采集目录为 `bench_dump`。"

msgid ""
"Use `msprobe graph_visualize` to build or compare graphs, then open the "
"generated `*.vis.db` file(s) with TensorBoard (`tb_graph_ascend` plugin)."
msgstr ""
"使用 `msprobe graph_visualize` 构建或对比图，然后通过 TensorBoard（`tb_graph_ascend` "
"插件）打开生成的 `*.vis.db` 文件。"

msgid "# MSProbe Debugging Guide"
msgstr "# MSProbe 调试指南"

msgid "## 0. Background Concepts"
msgstr "## 0. 背景概念"

msgid ""
"- **L0**: dumps tensors at the module level and generates `construct.json` so that visualization tools can rebuild the network structure. A model or submodule handle must be passed in.\n"
"- **L1**: collects operator-level statistics only, which is suitable for lightweight troubleshooting.\n"
"- **mix**: captures both structural information and operator statistics, which is useful when you need both graph reconstruction and numerical comparisons."
msgstr ""
"- **L0**：在模块级别转储张量，并生成 `construct.json`，以便可视化工具重建网络结构。必须传入模型或子模块句柄。\n"
"- **L1**：仅收集算子级别的统计信息，适用于轻量级问题排查。\n"
"- **mix**：同时捕获结构信息和算子统计信息，适用于需要同时进行图重建和数值比较的场景。"

msgid "## 1. Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 1. 前提条件"

msgid "### 1.1 Install `msprobe`"
msgstr "### 1.1 安装 `msprobe`"

msgid "### 1.2 Graph mode dump (optional)"
msgstr "### 1.2 图模式转储（可选）"

msgid "1. Install `aclgraph_dump` from source code:"
msgstr "1. 从源代码安装 `aclgraph_dump`："

msgid "## 2. Collecting Data with `msprobe`"
msgstr "## 2. 使用 `msprobe` 收集数据"

msgid "### 2.1 Prepare the dump configuration content"
msgstr "### 2.1 准备转储配置内容"

msgid ""
"- Pass the config object directly through `--additional-config.dump_config`.\n"
"- Pass a config file path through `--additional-config.dump_config_path`."
msgstr ""
"- 通过 `--additional-config.dump_config` 直接传入配置对象。\n"
"- 通过 `--additional-config.dump_config_path` 传入配置文件路径。"

msgid ""
"- `scope` (list[str]): In PyTorch PyNative scenarios this field restricts "
"the dump range. Provide two module or API names that follow the tool's "
"naming convention to lock a range; only data between the two names will be "
"dumped. Examples:"
msgstr ""
"- `scope` (list[str])：在 PyTorch PyNative 场景下，此字段限制转储范围。提供两个符合工具命名约定的模块或 API "
"名称来锁定一个范围；仅转储这两个名称之间的数据。示例："

msgid ""
"- `list` (list[str]): Custom operator list. Options include:\n"
"    - Supply the full names of specific APIs in PyTorch pynative scenarios to only dump those APIs. Example: `\"list\": [\"Tensor.permute.1.forward\", \"Tensor.transpose.2.forward\", \"Torch.relu.3.forward\"]`.\n"
"    - When `level=mix`, you can provide module names so that the dump expands to everything produced while the module is running. Example: `\"list\": [\"Module.module.language_model.encoder.layers.0.mlp.ParallelMlp.forward.0\"]`.\n"
"    - Provide a substring such as `\"list\": [\"relu\"]` to dump every API whose name contains the substring. When `level=mix`, modules whose names contain the substring are also expanded."
msgstr ""
"- `list` (list[str])：自定义算子列表。选项包括：\n"
"    - 在 PyTorch pynative 场景下，提供特定 API 的全名以仅转储这些 API。示例：`\"list\": [\"Tensor.permute.1.forward\", \"Tensor.transpose.2.forward\", \"Torch.relu.3.forward\"]`。\n"
"    - 当 `level=mix` 时，可以提供模块名称，以便转储扩展到模块运行时产生的所有内容。示例：`\"list\": [\"Module.module.language_model.encoder.layers.0.mlp.ParallelMlp.forward.0\"]`。\n"
"    - 提供子字符串，例如 `\"list\": [\"relu\"]`，以转储名称中包含该子字符串的所有 API。当 `level=mix` 时，名称中包含该子字符串的模块也会被扩展。"

msgid ""
"Example configuration:\n"
"eager mode:"
msgstr ""
"配置示例：\n"
"即时模式："

msgid "## 3. Enable `msprobe` in vllm-ascend"
msgstr "## 3. 在 vllm-ascend 中启用 `msprobe`"

msgid ""
"1. Start vLLM and pass the dump config content through `--additional-"
"config`:"
msgstr "1. 启动 vLLM 并通过 `--additional-config` 传入转储配置内容："

msgid "## 4. Send requests and collect dumps"
msgstr "## 4. 发送请求并收集转储"

msgid "1. Send inference requests as usual, for example:"
msgstr "1. 像往常一样发送推理请求，例如："

msgid ""
"2. Each request drives the sequence `msprobe: start -> forward -> stop -> "
"step`. The runner invokes `step()` on every code path, so you always get a "
"complete dataset even if inference returns early."
msgstr ""
"2. 每个请求驱动序列 `msprobe: start -> forward -> stop -> step`。运行器在每个代码路径上调用 "
"`step()`，因此即使推理提前返回，您也始终能获得完整的数据集。"

msgid ""
"3. Dump files are written into `dump_path`. They usually contain:\n"
"   - Tensor files grouped by operator/module.\n"
"   - `dump.json`, which records metadata such as dtype, shape, min/max, and `requires_grad`.\n"
"   - `construct.json`, which is generated when `level` is `L0` or `mix` (required for visualization)."
msgstr ""
"3. 转储文件写入 `dump_path`。它们通常包含：\n"
"   - 按算子/模块分组的张量文件。\n"
"   - `dump.json`，记录元数据，如 dtype、shape、min/max 和 `requires_grad`。\n"
"   - `construct.json`，当 `level` 为 `L0` 或 `mix` 时生成（可视化所需）。"

msgid ""
"Example directory layout:\n"
"   eager mode:"
msgstr ""
"示例目录结构：\n"
"   即时模式："

msgid ""
"- `rank`: Device ID. Each card writes its data to the corresponding `rank{ID}` directory. In non-distributed scenarios the directory is simply named `rank`.\n"
"   - `dump_tensor_data`: Tensor payloads that were collected.\n"
"   - `dump.json`: Statistics for the forward data of each API or module, including names, dtype, shape, max, min, mean, L2 norm (square root of the L2 variance), and CRC-32 when `summary_mode=\"md5\"`. See [dump.json file description](#dumpjson-file-description) for details.\n"
"   - `dump_error_info.log`: Present only when the dump tool encountered an error and records the failure log.\n"
"   - `stack.json`: Call stacks for APIs/modules.\n"
"   - `construct.json`: Hierarchical structure description. Empty when `level=L1`."
msgstr ""
"- `rank`：设备ID。每张卡将其数据写入对应的 `rank{ID}` 目录。在非分布式场景下，目录直接命名为 `rank`。\n"
"   - `dump_tensor_data`：收集到的张量载荷。\n"
"   - `dump.json`：每个API或模块前向数据的统计信息，包括名称、数据类型、形状、最大值、最小值、均值、L2范数（L2方差的平方根），以及当 `summary_mode=\"md5\"` 时的CRC-32。详见 [dump.json文件说明](#dumpjson-file-description)。\n"
"   - `dump_error_info.log`：仅当转储工具遇到错误时存在，记录失败日志。\n"
"   - `stack.json`：API/模块的调用栈。\n"
"   - `construct.json`：层次结构描述。当 `level=L1` 时为空。"

msgid ""
"- `dump.json`: Statistics for the forward data of each API or module, "
"including names, dtype, shape, max, min, mean, L2 norm (square root of the "
"L2 variance), and CRC-32 when `summary_mode=\"md5\"`. See [dump.json file "
"description](#dumpjson-file-description) for details."
msgstr ""
"- `dump.json`：每个API或模块前向数据的统计信息，包括名称、数据类型、形状、最大值、最小值、均值、L2范数（L2方差的平方根），以及当 "
"`summary_mode=\"md5\"` 时的CRC-32。详见 [dump.json文件说明](#dumpjson-file-"
"description)。"

msgid "## 5. Analyze the results"
msgstr "## 5. 分析结果"

msgid "### 5.1 Prerequisites"
msgstr "### 5.1 前提条件"

msgid "### 5.2 Visualization"
msgstr "### 5.2 可视化"

msgid ""
"1. Ensure dump data is visualization-ready:\n"
"   - Dump level must be `L0` or `mix` so `construct.json` is non-empty.\n"
"   - Each rank directory should contain `dump.json`, `stack.json`, and `construct.json`."
msgstr ""
"1. 确保转储数据已准备好进行可视化：\n"
"   - 转储级别必须为 `L0` 或 `mix`，以确保 `construct.json` 非空。\n"
"   - 每个rank目录应包含 `dump.json`、`stack.json` 和 `construct.json`。"

msgid ""
"2. Choose command mode:\n"
"   - Single-graph build:"
msgstr ""
"2. 选择命令模式：\n"
"   - 单图构建："

msgid "- Graph comparison:"
msgstr "- 图对比："

msgid ""
"- Common optional flags:\n"
"     - `-oc` / `--overflow_check`: enable overflow marking\n"
"     - `-fm` / `--fuzzy_match`: enable fuzzy matching for node mapping\n"
"     - `-lm` / `--layer_mapping [mapping.yaml]`: cross-framework/layer mapping compare\n"
"     - `-tensor_log`: print per-node compare log (tensor dump scenarios)\n"
"     - `-progress_log`: print detailed progress log"
msgstr ""
"- 通用可选标志：\n"
"     - `-oc` / `--overflow_check`：启用溢出标记\n"
"     - `-fm` / `--fuzzy_match`：启用节点映射的模糊匹配\n"
"     - `-lm` / `--layer_mapping [mapping.yaml]`：跨框架/层映射对比\n"
"     - `-tensor_log`：打印每个节点的对比日志（张量转储场景）\n"
"     - `-progress_log`：打印详细的进度日志"

msgid ""
"3. Path granularity is auto-detected by `graph_visualize`:\n"
"   - Single-rank: `.../step0/rank0`\n"
"   - Multi-rank (batch): `.../step0`\n"
"   - Multi-step (batch): dump root path containing `step*`"
msgstr ""
"3. `graph_visualize` 自动检测路径粒度：\n"
"   - 单rank：`.../step0/rank0`\n"
"   - 多rank（批量）：`.../step0`\n"
"   - 多步（批量）：包含 `step*` 的转储根路径"

msgid ""
"4. Output files:\n"
"   - Single-graph build: `build_{timestamp}.vis.db`\n"
"   - Graph comparison: `compare_{timestamp}.vis.db`"
msgstr ""
"4. 输出文件：\n"
"   - 单图构建：`build_{timestamp}.vis.db`\n"
"   - 图对比：`compare_{timestamp}.vis.db`"

msgid "5. Launch TensorBoard with the output directory:"
msgstr "5. 使用输出目录启动 TensorBoard："

msgid ""
"6. In the visualization UI, inspect structure and numeric differences:\n"
"   - Switch rank/step to locate unstable nodes quickly.\n"
"   - Use search/filter to focus on target ops/modules.\n"
"   - For compare mode, prioritize highlighted high-difference nodes and trace surrounding I/O/parameters."
msgstr ""
"6. 在可视化界面中，检查结构和数值差异：\n"
"   - 切换 rank/step 以快速定位不稳定节点。\n"
"   - 使用搜索/过滤功能聚焦于目标操作/模块。\n"
"   - 对于对比模式，优先处理高亮显示的高差异节点，并追踪其周围的输入/输出/参数。"

msgid "## 6. Troubleshooting"
msgstr "## 6. 故障排除"

msgid ""
"- `RuntimeError: Please enforce eager mode`: Restart vLLM and add the `--enforce-eager` flag.\n"
"- No dump files: Confirm that the JSON path is correct and every node has write permission. In distributed scenarios set `keep_all_ranks` so that every rank writes its own dump.\n"
"- Dumps are too large: Start with a `statistics` task to locate abnormal tensors, then narrow the scope with `scope`/`list`/`tensor_list`, `filters`, `token_range`, etc."
msgstr ""
"- `RuntimeError: Please enforce eager mode`：重启 vLLM 并添加 `--enforce-eager` 标志。\n"
"- 没有转储文件：确认 JSON 路径正确且每个节点都有写入权限。在分布式场景中，设置 `keep_all_ranks` 以便每个 rank 写入自己的转储。\n"
"- 转储文件过大：从 `statistics` 任务开始，定位异常张量，然后使用 `scope`/`list`/`tensor_list`、`filters`、`token_range` 等缩小范围。"

msgid "## Appendix"
msgstr "## 附录"

msgid "### dump.json file description"
msgstr "### dump.json 文件说明"

msgid "#### L0 level"
msgstr "#### L0 级别"

msgid ""
"- `Module.conv2.Conv2d.forward.0`: Forward data of the module. `input_args` "
"represents positional inputs, `input_kwargs` represents keyword inputs, "
"`output` stores forward outputs, and `parameters` stores weights/biases."
msgstr ""
"- `Module.conv2.Conv2d.forward.0`：模块的前向数据。`input_args` 表示位置输入，`input_kwargs`"
" 表示关键字输入，`output` 存储前向输出，`parameters` 存储权重/偏置。"

msgid "#### L1 level"
msgstr "#### L1 级别"

msgid ""
"- `Functional.relu.0.forward`: Forward data of the API. `input_args` are "
"positional inputs, `input_kwargs` are keyword inputs, and `output` stores "
"the forward outputs."
msgstr ""
"- `Functional.relu.0.forward`：API 的前向数据。`input_args` 是位置输入，`input_kwargs` "
"是关键字输入，`output` 存储前向输出。"

msgid "#### mix level"
msgstr "#### mix 级别"

msgid ""
"| Field       | Description"
"                                                                                                                                                                                                 "
"| Required | Eager Mode | Graph Mode |"
msgstr ""
"| 字段       | 描述"
"                                                                                                                                                                                                         "
"| 必填     | 即时模式   | 图模式     |"

msgid ""
"| `task`      | Type of dump task. Common PyTorch values include "
"`\"statistics\"` and `\"tensor\"`. A statistics task collects tensor "
"statistics (mean, variance, max, min, etc.) while a tensor task captures "
"arbitrary tensors. |    Yes   |      ✅       |      ✅       |"
msgstr ""
"| `task`      | 转储任务类型。常见的 PyTorch 值包括 `\"statistics\"` 和 "
"`\"tensor\"`。统计任务收集张量统计信息（均值、方差、最大值、最小值等），而张量任务捕获任意张量。 |    是    |      ✅"
"       |      ✅       |"

msgid ""
"| `dump_path` | Directory where dump results are stored. When omitted, "
"`msprobe` uses its default path."
"                                                                                                                     "
"|    No    |      ✅       |      ✅       |"
msgstr ""
"| `dump_path` | 存储转储结果的目录。省略时，`msprobe` 使用其默认路径。"
"                                                                                                                     "
"|    否    |      ✅       |      ✅       |"

msgid ""
"| `rank`      | Ranks to sample. An empty list collects every rank. For "
"single-card tasks, you must set this field to `[]`."
"                                                                                                 "
"|    No    |      ✅       |      ✅       |"
msgstr ""
"| `rank`      | 要采样的卡号。空列表表示收集所有卡号。对于单卡任务，必须将此字段设置为 `[]`。"
"                                                                                                 "
"|    否    |      ✅       |      ✅       |"

msgid ""
"| `step`      | Token iteration(s) to sample. An empty list means every "
"iteration."
"                                                                                                                                         "
"|    No    |      ✅       |      ❌       |"
msgstr ""
"| `step`      | 要采样的 token 迭代次数。空列表表示每次迭代。"
"                                                                                                                                         "
"|    否    |      ✅       |      ❌       |"

msgid ""
"| `level`     | Dump level string (`\"L0\"`, `\"L1\"`, or `\"mix\"`). `L0` "
"targets `nn.Module`, `L1` targets `torch.api`, and `mix` collects both."
"                                                                                 "
"|    Yes   |      ✅       |      ✅       |"
msgstr ""
"| `level`     | 转储级别字符串（`\"L0\"`、`\"L1\"` 或 `\"mix\"`）。`L0` 针对 "
"`nn.Module`，`L1` 针对 `torch.api`，`mix` 收集两者。"
"                                                                                 "
"|    是    |      ✅       |      ✅       |"

msgid ""
"| `async_dump`| Whether to enable asynchronous dump (supported for PyTorch "
"`statistics`/`tensor` tasks). Defaults to `false`."
"                                                                                              "
"|    No    |      ✅       |      ❌       |"
msgstr ""
"| `async_dump`| 是否启用异步转储（支持 PyTorch `statistics`/`tensor` 任务）。默认为 `false`。"
"                                                                                              "
"|    否    |      ✅       |      ❌       |"

msgid ""
"| `scope`     | Module range to sample. An empty list collects every module."
"                                                                                                                                                "
"|    No    |      ✅       |      ❌       |"
msgstr ""
"| `scope`     | 要采样的模块范围。空列表表示收集所有模块。"
